# Geharde SSH configuratie — Ubuntu Server
# Gegenereerd na toepassing van ssh-hardening.sh

Port 22
Protocol 2

# Authenticatie
PermitRootLogin no
MaxAuthTries 3
PubkeyAuthentication yes
PasswordAuthentication no
PermitEmptyPasswords no
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no

# Sessie timeout
ClientAliveInterval 600
ClientAliveCountMax 0

# Overig
X11Forwarding no
PrintMotd no
AcceptEnv LANG LC_*
Subsystem sftp /usr/lib/openssh/sftp-server

